人加租<br />\n應該做多幾年就退休"},{"pid":"73ea729f2c0e9bf9c9d218f658a39eda4cedce98","tid":518514,"uid":56453,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T02:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有幾年冇試過係香港使多過1千買野&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/clown.png&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt; <br />\n日本就唔同，多多錢都肯使&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n去日本旅行洗錢真係洗得開心過香港<br />\n一來價錢合理，二來物有(超)所值<br />\n淨係講食已經贏左啦，係香港食飯目的多數都係吊命，完全無乜享受"},{"pid":"860954d03aa21fb14581624031f90e32906df0b8","tid":518514,"uid":45645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T02:54:08.000Z","msg":"抵死!"},{"pid":"24c85d061c1a994f644d767f1091fdd1c902b532","tid":518514,"uid":93784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T03:06:00.000Z","msg":"金鋪一個月300萬 點賺?<br />\n仲未計電費人工等開支"},{"pid":"44b5610ff8d85b35b39f883fa701434574c2e6d4","tid":518514,"uid":63977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T03:08:27.000Z","msg":"關乜事<br />\n一條街幾十間金舖,<br />\n供過於求,<br />\n咁耐都唔執先係香港奇跡 !"},{"pid":"40a066a23314ae48f61ee71b4cc1fc3520760c04","tid":518514,"uid":162303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T03:14:07.000Z","msg":"地產aa老友講，<br />\n根本利是封店即係短租果d，全部都係間鋪自己個業主做番，所以樓上唔擔心！"},{"pid":"b7b012adcfa328922a091506e74cc8545b8d08f2","tid":518514,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17f60144c20fb1dea4b4908df48c1ea7bf2482b3","tid":518514,"uid":22069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T02:45:43.000Z","msg":"老豆賣鞋賣左30幾年<br />\n睇住佢生意愈黎愈差<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要比人加租<br />\n應該做多幾年就退休"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T03:15:58.000Z","msg":"mltd asos 大把方法買<br />\n仲駛買你on99 貴鞋"},{"pid":"e3531e56c70e1c1042ee538a18169403e457d239","tid":518514,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecf833c0e3202249d768b5e9786d573d8abfdd5a","tid":518514